node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by camryn harris on July 18, 2021 tagging @makeupbyjess, and @doegirlnezz. May be an image of 2 people and indoor.

node.text:
i am honestly still speechless. 🥺 i dont have any pictures, my voice is almost gone cause i was just screaming the entire time, so i recorded NOTHING🤣🤣🤣 
•being apart of the show is one thing, but actually watching the show is a completely different experience! the amount of stress, anxiety, and nerves dancers go through is always overwhelming. we work so hard to entertain thousands, and THAT is exactly what i saw on stage last night! 🔥
(i see now that everyone loves to surprise me🤣)
•this was a surprise of a lifetime! my jaw dropped straight to the floor while watching them🤩. and especially while watching the tribute performance💜🥺 
•to @liberian_girl.aaliyah , @iaamkhelsii_ , and @_thatdollmanii 
just like i told yall… YALL UNDERSTOOD THE ASSIGNMENT!!!! 🤩yall completely blew my mind away and i couldnt be more proud! 🥺🥺🥺
and miss @daniellenstamper !!! GIRLLLL, when i say took my breath away. TOOK IT AWAY. that was the cherry on top for me. thank you so much for making time out of your schedule to do this for me🥺
and to @mrs_d2u , i cant thank you enough for this tribute. i honestly felt like i started losing my passion for dance because of dealing with so much in life, but this reminded me how far i’ve come and ignited something in me i hadn’t felt in a while 😌. so i thank you whole heartedly for taking the time and energy to put on this beautiful showcase! 💜 thank you again to my wonderful DD4L family and everyone who came to help with this amazing show! i love yall so much!! 🤞🏽💜💜💜😘😘 #bestnightever #dd4l

•happy mothers day to my best friend💜 
no matter the time, day, or place you will always be there for me. the way you care for not only our family but for others is unmatched! i love you so much and i am so grateful to have you as a mom🥺. @thereal_mimiharris
